<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ حَسّان بن محرش.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال قُتَيبة:</span> لقيتُه بمَكَّة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>